      "data": {
        "identity": {
          "graphId": "tutorial-getting-started"
        },
        "markdown": "## Why This Changed\n\nThe older getting-started graph behaved like a broad launcher full of mixed legacy links. The current shelf is stronger when each graph tells the truth about what it is for and points directly at the public artifact it opens.\n\nUse this graph as the clean handoff into the modern tutorial path."
